<!-- Definition  and medical uses -->
'''苯巴比妥'''（{{lang|en|Phenobarbital}}或{{lang|en|Phenobarbitone}}），也稱為'''魯米那'''（{{lang|en|Luminal}}），是一種[[巴比妥|巴比妥]]類的[[鎮靜劑|鎮靜劑]]及[[安眠藥|安眠藥]]。該藥物是[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]對於[[開發中國家|開發中國家]]治療特定[[癲癇|癲癇]]的建議用藥<ref name=Ila2012>{{cite journal|last=Ilangaratne|first=NB|author2=Mannakkara, NN |author3=Bell, GS |author4= Sander, JW |title=Phenobarbital: missing in action.|journal=Bulletin of the World Health Organization|date=Dec 1, 2012|volume=90|issue=12|pages=871-871A|pmid=23284189|doi=10.2471/BLT.12.113183}}</ref>。已開發國家則通常專門用來治療[[新生兒|新生兒]]癲癇發作<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brodie|first1=MJ|last2=Kwan|first2=P|title=Current position of phenobarbital in epilepsy and its future.|journal=Epilepsia|date=December 2012|volume=53 Suppl 8|pages=40-6|pmid=23205961}}</ref>，成人及青少年則建議使用其他藥物<ref>{{cite web|title=The epilepsies: the diagnosis and management of the epilepsies in adults and children in primary and secondary care NICE guidelines [CG137]|website=National Institute for Health and Care Excellence|accessdate=14 August 2015|date=January 2012}}</ref>。苯巴比妥可透過靜脈注射、肌肉注射，或口服給藥<ref name=AHFS2015/>。通常[[癲癇重積狀態|癲癇重積狀態]]會以注射方式給藥，因為藥效作用較迅速<ref name=AHFS2015/>。苯巴比妥有時會被用於治療[[失眠症|失眠症]]、[[焦慮症|焦慮症]]、[[藥物戒斷症|藥物戒斷症]]，以及手術輔助用途<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Phenobarbital|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/phenobarbital.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=Aug 14, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906225702/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/phenobarbital.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。靜脈注射給藥的藥效通常會在五分鐘內作用，口服則需半個小時<ref name=AHFS2015/>。藥效則通常會維持4小時至2天之久<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Marx2010>{{cite book|last1=Marx|first1=John A.|title=Rosen's emergency medicine : concepts and clinical practice|date=2010|publisher=Mosby/Elsevier|location=Philadelphia|isbn=9780323054720|page=1352|edition=7|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=u7TNcpCeqx8C&pg=PA1352|access-date=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305025648/https://books.google.ca/books?id=u7TNcpCeqx8C&pg=PA1352|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- History, society and culture -->
苯巴比妥在1912年發現，是仍在使用的{{le|抗驚厥劑|anti-seizure medication}}中歷史最久的<ref>{{cite book|last1=Stevens|first1=George M. Brenner, Craig W.|title=Pharmacology|date=2013|publisher=Elsevier/Saunders|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=9781455702787|page=204|edition=4th|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=Cd39SN6OBiMC&pg=PA204|access-date=2016-03-23|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023070746/http://books.google.ca/books?id=Cd39SN6OBiMC&pg=PA204|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Engel|first1=Jerome|title=Epilepsy : a comprehensive textbook|date=2008|publisher=Wolters Kluwer Health/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia|isbn=9780781757775|page=1431|edition=2nd ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=3ZktoDp7tZoC&pg=PA1431|access-date=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305041712/https://books.google.ca/books?id=3ZktoDp7tZoC&pg=PA1431|dead-url=no}}</ref>。苯巴比妥是[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]中的藥品，是基礎醫療必備的藥品之一<ref name="essentialWHO">{{cite web | date = March 2005 | url = http://whqlibdoc.who.int/hq/2005/a87017_eng.pdf | title = WHO Model List of Essential Medicines | format = PDF | publisher = World Health Organization | accessdate = 2006-03-12 | archive-date = 2007-02-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070212145830/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/hq/2005/a87017_eng.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其價格也是抗驚厥劑中最便宜的，一年約需要美金5元<ref name=Poor2012/>。不過因為苯巴比妥在一些國家是{{le|管制用藥|Controlled drug}}，因此在這些國家可能不容易取得<ref name=Poor2012>{{cite journal|last=Newton|first=CR|title=Epilepsy in poor regions of the world.|journal=Lancet|date=29 September 2012|volume=380|issue=9848|pages=1193–201|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(12)61381-6|pmid=23021288}}</ref>。

==性质==
纯品苯巴比妥是无色有光泽的结晶性粉末，无臭，味微苦，微溶于水，易溶于[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[氯仿|氯仿]]和[[苯|苯]]，熔点174℃。[[警示性质标准词列表|警示标准词]]有：{{R24}}。

苯巴比妥与[[硝酸钾|硝酸钾]]及硫酸共热可发生[[硝化反应|硝化反应]]，生成黄色硝基化合物。可与硫酸与[[亚硝酸钠|亚硝酸钠]]反应，生成橙黄色产物，并随即变为橙红色。可与[[甲醛|甲醛]]和[[硫酸|硫酸]]反应，生成玫瑰红色产物。<ref name="药物分析">{{cite book |title=药物分析|url=https://archive.org/details/yaowufenxi0000unse_q7d2|publisher=人民卫生出版社|year=2007|location=北京| pages=[https://archive.org/details/yaowufenxi0000unse_q7d2/page/119 119]-121| isbn=978-7-117-08983-8}}</ref>

==合成路线==
苯[[乙酸乙酯|乙酸乙酯]]与[[碳酸二乙酯|碳酸二乙酯]]在碱作用下缩合生成[[苯基|苯基]][[丙二酸二乙酯|丙二酸二乙酯]]，然后与[[氯乙烷|氯乙烷]]在[[乙醇钠|乙醇钠]]存在下再次缩合，得到[[苯基|苯基]][[乙基|乙基]][[丙二酸二乙酯|丙二酸二乙酯]]，再与[[尿素|尿素]]环合，即生成苯巴比妥。<ref name="药物分析" />

